A shining vibrancy with modest undertones of urban sophistication in the Ithaca dining room welcomes Zen-like luxury into your space with a simple smile. Constructed of wood solids and oak veneers in a natural finish, the 72" rectangular tabletop extends to 90" with an included leaf to accommodate larger parties. Four large legs give this piece an impressive presence that balances perfectly with its subtle aesthetic. Each side chair features a ladder back and an upholstered seat in beige, its soft fabric complementing the gentle curve of the frame.
